{"tid":495644,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要叫女護士／社工做姑娘？","createTime":"2017-12-11T01:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T07:48:19.000Z","uid":100391,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"171a09ec2838e46f32dc51c100813aa411fde886","tid":495644,"uid":100391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"姑娘呢個term又肉麻又old school<br />\n根本同呢2個行業都唔關事<br />\n又唔見我地會叫啲女sales／老師做姑娘<br />\n<br />\n姑娘係解未婚後生女 做咩要叫啲中女護士姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明就應該要叫姑婆<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解我地又唔會叫男護士／社工 做小哥／少年／相公<br />\n有時仲聽人叫男護士做男姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩鳩"},{"pid":"5845946269221d0d903d538652b1534dd1a8b434","tid":495644,"uid":21488,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"男姑娘 之前聽過人嗌 個時都笑到仆街😂"},{"pid":"30e2103488e54525222fcd1dd2ff386a90f878cc","tid":495644,"uid":23495,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:18:13.000Z","msg":"姑娘 對應係公子<br />\n而唔係咩小哥，相公囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b296d54654a4f2bd3f334876e358150b715505eb","tid":495644,"uid":150698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"女小哥 女少年 女相公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfcc937183e1879902815cb4de7c52f9a06b303","tid":495644,"uid":100391,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男姑娘 之前聽過人嗌 個時都笑到仆街😂</blockquote><br />\n男人老狗大學讀nursing真係好撚悲哀 要比人叫成世姑娘"},{"pid":"e77098c716008eb0364a3cd7c43a90973cd34291","tid":495644,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"唔通叫佢臭雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p